OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1773691869
OL,3,CBusinesses to be given #3k to employ
OL,4,Cyoung people out of work
OL,6,FBusinesses are set to receive #3,000
OL,7,Ffor every young person they hire, who
OL,8,Fis aged 18 to 24 and has been
OL,9,Fsearching for a job for six months or
OL,10,Fmore.
OL,12,FThe funding, part of a "new deal" for
OL,13,Fyoung people set to be announced by
OL,14,FWork and Pensions Secretary Pat
OL,15,FMcFadden on Monday, is aimed at
OL,16,Fcreating 200,000 jobs.
OL,18,FAround 60,000 people are expected to
OL,19,Fbe supported by the proposals.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
