OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1773691869
OL,3,CBusinesses to be given #3k to employ
OL,4,Cyoung people out of work
OL,6,FThe latest figures show that over 1 in
OL,7,F5 young people are not in work,
OL,8,Ftraining or education - a figure which
OL,9,Fhas sharply risen in recent years.
OL,11,FMcFadden will also announce a new
OL,12,Fapprenticeship incentive, under which
OL,13,Fsmall and medium-sized businesses are
OL,14,Fpaid #2,000 for every worker aged
OL,15,Fbetween 16 and 24-years-old they take
OL,16,Fon.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1773691869
OL,3,CBusinesses to be given #3k to employ
OL,4,Cyoung people out of work
OL,6,FThis plan has been backed by celebrity
OL,7,Fchef Tom Kerridge, who employs
OL,8,Fapprentices in his restaurants and
OL,9,Fsaid he was "pleased" McFadden made
OL,10,Fthis a priority.
OL,12,F"I've trained apprentices in my
OL,13,Frestaurants, and I know what a great
OL,14,Fstart it gives them in their careers,
OL,15,Fand these incentives will give our
OL,16,Findustry a great boost," he said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
