CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1773691869
OL,3,CBusinesses to be given #3k to employ
OL,4,Cyoung people out of work
OL,6,FThere have been some reports that this
OL,7,Fscheme will replace existing
OL,8,Fprogrammes for apprenticeships, but
OL,9,Fthe full details have not yet been
OL,10,Frevealed.
OL,12,FITV News has previously reported on
OL,13,Fthe government's Youth Job Guarantee
OL,14,Fscheme, which provides around 40,000
OL,15,Fpaid work placements for 18 to 21-year-
OL,16,Folds who have been unemployed for more
OL,17,Fthan 18 months.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1773691869
OL,3,CBusinesses to be given #3k to employ
OL,4,Cyoung people out of work
OL,6,FIt is understood that Monday's
OL,7,Fannouncement will also see the scheme
OL,8,Fexpanded, from the current age range
OL,9,Fof 18 to 21, to those up to 24 years
OL,10,Fold.
OL,12,FSpeaking ahead of the announcement,
OL,13,FMcFadden promised that his measures
OL,14,Fwould "significantly reverse the
OL,15,Fincrease we inherited in those not in
OL,16,Feducation, employment or training",
OL,17,Fdespite claims from the Conservatives
OL,18,Fthat their plan would damage
OL,19,Fbusinesses in the long run.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1773691869
OL,3,CBusinesses to be given #3k to employ
OL,4,Cyoung people out of work
OL,6,FThe Shadow Work and Pensions Secretary
OL,7,FHelen Whately said on Sunday that the
OL,8,Fcosts associated with the new scheme
OL,9,Fcould lead to businesses being taxed
OL,10,F"out of existence".
OL,12,FShe said the Conservatives would
OL,13,Ftackle youth unemployment by "cutting
OL,14,Fbusiness rates for thousands of high
OL,15,Fstreet businesses" - a policy her
OL,16,Fparty says would "create jobs".
OL,18,F"That's the way to create real
OL,19,Fopportunities for young people and get
OL,20,FBritain working again," she said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
